{"id": "1cc4712c8da18cedf6dcdebd0b3220f4020319bc52ada5bd050ce00b56563851", "item_id": "7a5088454f:0", "text": "Thresholds an input color pattern to create a black and white mask. The falloff will define a gradual transition from black to white. The output is always between 0 and 1."}
{"id": "974df556381245f5ba48330316a517b1bce5fb6acccda7f9c2e04b768f8749fd", "item_id": "7a5088454f:3", "text": "The color pattern you would like to threshold."}
{"id": "ce4683e7013a18cdf3d224bfcb4e9594ea8f559e946a837c633defe7d3c32172", "item_id": "7a5088454f:4", "text": "Channel"}
{"id": "e5d14eb636fbca0f8913bcc797861fa371701997055b24516667d4eb27ecad15", "item_id": "7a5088454f:5", "text": "The input channel this node will operate on:"}
{"id": "cd34c511cdfc1990feb9eff574df5570ce338a17bcbc534838636b431ff5ece4", "item_id": "7a5088454f:6", "text": "0: Red"}
{"id": "163df6c60faaee4fc415dc8953b781dfbb5ab4090ec0b95f39288020c5165c9b", "item_id": "7a5088454f:7", "text": "1: Green"}
{"id": "f59e74f31dd1d4e515724043c79a5e1a923d2826455bf0480b95231191b41853", "item_id": "7a5088454f:8", "text": "2: Blue"}
{"id": "7d1f6c34d90e1940cc08d27a27628090ad67ee6fc4fa064077807b18d0277399", "item_id": "7a5088454f:9", "text": "3: Luminance"}
{"id": "e86fe5b507e95375a3b5c523e75c7cf2cfa78a06b46d1d495991f39a77cf5db2", "item_id": "7a5088454f:10", "text": "4: Average"}
{"id": "0da627ada476c179bb6421d267cb6de8c9f770a2274b5d673d898e33cea29247", "item_id": "7a5088454f:11", "text": "Threshold"}
{"id": "6ed46e0deb1f04d37689c466f4df5d8043e78a2513f1cdeb914b8a2cbd98c351", "item_id": "7a5088454f:12", "text": "The value at which the transition from black to white will take place."}
{"id": "faf96b1acee1c9942c64d76779de47157749612626169b417c3256de3c472461", "item_id": "7a5088454f:13", "text": "Transition Width"}
{"id": "4a520d2aa820fab07c5609b663c6082324e0220277518406335f593cab5bbfea", "item_id": "7a5088454f:14", "text": "This control allows you to create a sharp or progressive transitions. The transition width is centered on the threshold value."}
{"id": "f60339bcf09112c09cd84e78c80246d8591ef1a5b7c2340bd887b2b0bc3a3bd6", "item_id": "7a5088454f:15", "text": "Transition Profile"}
{"id": "0f20f3505dd7af95a692feac32dfb0f22e7282177b31d507b29d0a30ca3d4aeb", "item_id": "7a5088454f:16", "text": "The interpolation from black to white can be computed with three different curves:"}
{"id": "b4d77402af8efc4f00ce3d5ce5bad1ad3141c9766a64fe484de0e6a26e23a961", "item_id": "7a5088454f:17", "text": "0: Linear"}
{"id": "9ef5076f8cdff7874b95296e999ecf366035ef8895c5b38867d74bf71f7e0280", "item_id": "7a5088454f:18", "text": "1: Smooth"}
{"id": "f89d91aaefc44c205771c0aab3a77b9d9da30ca10287be640f7fa3a878345a27", "item_id": "7a5088454f:19", "text": "2: Gaussian"}
{"id": "e857588daac5e8d45077b03fd4335b91d0e410985944b0d063300a5c1bce34bb", "item_id": "7a5088454f:22", "text": "The tresholded pattern as a monochrome color."}
{"id": "7ae85c2d0074f0b45ec3f98d2f40a5f79e86abedd6e35ab372b9d21772a2c28a", "item_id": "7a5088454f:24", "text": "The R channel result"}
{"id": "696353435479edc46a3e8ec45c217c084c9d249ddcb922a3445131f174d9c090", "item_id": "7a5088454f:26", "text": "The G channel result"}
{"id": "691964dd34e3c6e471f04289a508b02ddba69e7fd40aca1f59ebcba4d5401255", "item_id": "7a5088454f:28", "text": "The B channel result"}
{"id": "890f7aa1b6882bd3a2548401dd7ae638108b8010a3cbcc25974c005ba36f3048", "item_id": "7a5088454f:29", "text": "resultA"}
{"id": "95bd1216e8575541512f791f94b631bd5fb82801c6d76b4cdc1f19dd36d314d9", "item_id": "7a5088454f:30", "text": "If alpha is present and"}
{"id": "5e5cd018d92d4ab6d4bf33fd8dd3320a5aeb0c743a2b3a64760c3fa9dc14ec2e", "item_id": "7a5088454f:32", "text": "is connected it returns the channel after RGB. If RGB is not connected it returns the first channel."}
